These tools are for use with the XBOX 360 version of espgaluda 2.

-- audio.py --
arg: se.bin, located at:

D38939428346F0DE76461C7D1BFDF0A0/res/DISKDATA/SOUND/se.bin

and outputs extracted XMA audio samples. It can also repack those
samples into a new bin. It's worth noting that the game seems to be ok
with replacing the XMA samples with PCM WAV. As has been done with
se.bin in this repo which replaced the shrill shot sound with
something less harsh.

-- gfx.py --
arg: *.bin located at:

D38939428346F0DE76461C7D1BFDF0A0/res/DISKDATA/{ARCADE/BL/XB360}/*.bin

and outputs TGA+PNG extracted textures. It can also repack those
textures into a new bin.